@page "/"

<div class="container">
    <div class="row text-center my-5">
        <div class="col">
            <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to CrickoManager</h1>
            <p class="lead">National Cricket Board's Official Tournament Management System</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row my-4">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">Matches</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Schedule and manage cricket matches for the tournament. View upcoming and past matches.</p>
                    <a href="matches" class="btn btn-primary">Manage Matches</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <div class="card-header bg-success text-white">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">Live Scoreboard</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>View and update real-time scores for ongoing matches in the tournament.</p>
                    <a href="livescoreboard" class="btn btn-success">View Live Scores</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">Standings</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Check the current tournament standings, points table and team rankings.</p>
                    <a href="standings" class="btn btn-info">View Standings</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row my-5">
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header bg-secondary text-white">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">About CrickoManager</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>CrickoManager is the official tournament management system developed for the National Cricket Board. This system provides comprehensive tools for managing all aspects of cricket tournaments including:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Team and match management</li>
                        <li>Real-time score updates</li>
                        <li>Tournament standings and statistics</li>
                        <li>Comprehensive reporting</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>Tournament officials can efficiently organize matches, update scores, and monitor the progress of the tournament through this integrated platform.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
